The paper discusses recent advancements in artificial intelligence, including mathematically sound problem solvers and practical methods for learning sequence-processing programs. These topics are closely related to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper, with cs.AI being the most likely.
